# Technical Specification: Enterprise Risk Module - Content Analysis Pipeline

## 1. Overview
This module adds content-level analysis to the PeopleInsight platform for enterprise risk detection. The system analyzes Slack/Teams messages for specific risk patterns and routes flagged content to a review queue with context.

## 2. System Architecture

### 2.1 Updated Pipeline Architecture
```
Message Stream → NLP Preprocessing → Topic Classification → Risk Scoring → Alert Generation → Review Queue
      ↓               ↓                 ↓              ↓           ↓              ↓
Real-time API     Text Cleaning     Multi-label     Severity      Alert          Secure
Messages        Entity Extraction   Classification  Calculation   Assembly       Storage
```

### 2.2 Processing Flow Components
```
1. Message Ingestion (Real-time & Batch)
   - Slack Enterprise API (real-time events)
   - Microsoft Teams Graph API (real-time)
   - Historical message batch processing

2. NLP Pipeline
   - Text preprocessing & normalization
   - Entity recognition (companies, roles, etc.)
   - Pattern matching (regex & ML classifiers)

3. Risk Classification Engine
   - Topic taxonomy application
   - Multi-label classification
   - Confidence scoring

4. Alert Assembly & Routing
   - Severity tier calculation
   - Context gathering (5 messages before/after)
   - Secure storage with access controls

5. Review Queue Interface
   - HR/InfoSec reviewer dashboard
   - Audit logging
   - Escalation workflows
```

